[src:scim-provisioning-deep/lightweight-directory-access-protocol] The Extended Operation is a generic LDAP operation that can define new operations that were not part of the original protocol specification.
[src:scim-provisioning-deep/lightweight-directory-access-protocol] StartTLS is one of the most significant extensions.
